      {
        "type": "Markdown",
        "props": {
          "id": "Markdown-1773a213-1190-4411-8930-aeb41d280ac3",
          "text": "The Early Access Programme (EAP) enables customers to commit early to receive discounted pricing and access the recipe ahead of general release.\n\n## Benefits\n\nEAP partners receive numerous benefits:\n\n- Early access to recipe through canary releases\n- Input to roadmap prioritisation\n- Regular progress updates\n- Discounted pricing\n\n## Early-access fees\n\n- No setup fee\n- 25% discount ($36,000 / year)\n- Payable on delivery of each phase ($12,000 / phase)\n- 1st year only, then [standard license fee](/proposals/puck-platform-recipe/license)\n\n\n## Terms\n\nThe Early Access Programme is subject to terms and conditions.",
          "align": "left",
          "measured": true
        }
      },
